description.narrative: Some positive progress in advancing a multi-sectoral approach to early childhood development in Tunisia in 2019, although more efforts will be required to cover all key aspects of the national ECD strategy 2017-2025. Key results include the engagement of the private sector, a critical player in the dialogue on the quality of immunization services for children; and the engagement of multiple ministries at central and decentralised level for the development of the positive parenting programme, one of the key strategic orientations of the ECD strategy, with the participation of the private sector. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:21/01/2020
